item.title: CVE-2020-5667|2024-08-04T08:39:25.501Z -- studyplus%20inc. -- studyplus%20app
item.description: Studyplus App for Android v6.3.7 and earlier and Studyplus App for iOS v8.29.0 and earlier use a hard-coded API key for an external service. By exploiting this vulnerability, API key for an external service may be obtained by analyzing data in the app.
